<div class="prose-content max-w-3xl mb-8">
  <p>Our team works together to provide the best possible care for our patients. We are also fortunate to have GP Trainees and medical students attached to our practice — with a patient's consent, they may carry out consultations as part of their training.</p>
  <p>Some services at Leven Health Centre are provided by NHS Fife CTAC (Community Treatment and Care) staff. <strong>These appointments are booked via NHS Fife Reception at Leven Health Centre, not via Scoonie Medical Practice reception.</strong> This is noted in the relevant sections below.</p>
</div>

<section aria-labelledby="gp-heading" class="mb-10">
  <h2 id="gp-heading" class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-4">Doctors</h2>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    {% for member in team %}
    {% if member.category == "gp" %}
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-brand-primary rounded-lg p-4">
      <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-dark">{{ member.name }}</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-brand-primary mt-0.5">{{ member.role }}</p>
      {% if member.qualifications %}
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-mid mt-2 leading-relaxed">{{ member.qualifications }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section aria-labelledby="anp-heading" class="mb-10">
  <h2 id="anp-heading" class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Nurse Practitioners</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid mb-4">Our nurse practitioners treat many of the same conditions as GPs. Book via Scoonie Reception on <a href="tel:{{ site.phone | replace(' ', '') }}">{{ site.phone }}</a>.</p>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    {% for member in team %}
    {% if member.category == "anp" %}
    <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 border-l-4 border-l-teal-600 rounded-lg p-4">
      <p class="font-semibold text-neutral-dark">{{ member.name }}</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-teal-700 mt-0.5">{{ member.role }}</p>
      {% if member.qualifications %}
      <p class="text-xs text-neutral-mid mt-2 leading-relaxed">{{ member.qualifications }}</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

