<section aria-labelledby="pharmacy-heading" class="mb-10">
  <h2 id="pharmacy-heading" class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-dark mb-2">Pharmacy Team</h2>
  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid mb-4">Our practice pharmacist and NHS Fife pharmacy team manage medication reviews, prescribing support, and patient medication queries.</p>
